{"tid":208141,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"36歲方皓玟入紙結婚嫁日模男友","createTime":"2017-04-19T10:38:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-20T12:42:47.000Z","uid":28765,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"57e1146fc026b3f5bd792b07d8e5e5ebb007aabe","tid":208141,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T10:38:09.000Z","msg":"東網巨星<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n04月19日(三) 15:56   <br />\n<br />\n方皓玟結婚喇！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現年36歲藝人的方皓玟（原名吳嘉欣），一向甚少提及感情事。四月十日，一名報稱任職歌手的吳嘉欣入紙排期註冊結婚，在其擬結婚通知書上，吳嘉欣的出生日期與方皓玟相同，而男方則為37歲、報稱任職模特兒的日本人YASUDA, SHINGO（安田慎吾）。二人更申報同一住址。 <br />\n<br />\n東網聯絡上方皓玟，問她是否排期結婚、男友是否日本人，她則只用訊息報上一個「笑笑口」的EMOJI作回應。再追問下，她才表示：「多謝大家關心，感情事一向比較低調啲，多謝大家祝福，我會繼續努力，加油！紙都排緊期，係會結婚，只係我唔鍾意消費婚姻，所以感情一路低調，多謝你關心！」 <br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170419/mobile/bkn-20170419155610239-0419_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170419%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20170419155610239-0419_00862_001.html&d=mwjAj24IHyfJiBWsHz9aFv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=a340fd60\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170419/mobile/bkn-20170419155610239-0419_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"75db2aa29a4c3754f8714011678c83626ab65a8c","tid":208141,"uid":35336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T10:48:42.000Z","msg":"恭喜八両仔"},{"pid":"a41f196a7086385897e6f3ccc0ac703d3c183ac7","tid":208141,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T11:11:20.000Z","msg":"幾時到春卷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea65a2138c9f0583aa502556272bfe1e55c4696a","tid":208141,"uid":4180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T13:20:19.000Z","msg":"個老公幾靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf10a8b660993cd1ae9d700fb488a77fff8d128c","tid":208141,"uid":52654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T15:1